title: The Oh-So-Painfully-Close-to-Compleat Squeeze Collection
description:
Why the heck hasn&#039;t everyone&#039;s favorite obscure new-wave band appeared here before this torrent series?  Well, I&#039;ve been collecting Squeeze songs for 19 years, and here&#039;s my entire collection.  It includes all of their album releases (minus the "greatest hits"-type compilations), as well as some random tracks, some very difficult to find.

If you have any Squeeze that I do not have here, please please PLEASE make me aware of it!

Albums included:
* U.K. Squeeze
* Cool for Cats
* Argybargy
* East Side Story
* Sweets from a Stranger
* Difford & Tilbrook
* Cosi Fan Tutti Frutti
* Babylon and On
* Frank
* A Round & A Bout
* Play
* Some Fantastic Place
* Ridiculous
* Domino

PLUS an "assorted singles" directory (including over 50 singles from various complilation albums, singles, promos, etc.)

Please seed, and again, if you know where I can find something not here PLEASE let me know!  Thank you, and enjoy!
